  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Muhldorf was 77 kilo-- is 77 kilometers from Munich, on one side of Munich.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the other side of Munich is, is, is Dachau, just outside of Munich.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they went-- they went with a body full-- with a truck full of bodies to for the crematorium, because they saved them to take it out to the, to the pits.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on the way back, you filled it up with shoes, and, and clothes, and whatever there was necessary, sometimes food from Dachau.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day they just came in to the-- to the workshop and they said, can you spare any people, to the fellow who was in charge.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, yeah, we can spare some people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He knew what we were all about and what was, and a usual, regular trip to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I must tell you that I, I must have been half [INAUDIBLE] already myself because I knew that the truck was loaded with bodies and that some of the bodies was not completely dead.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the truck was running on, on, on wood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One of the trucks which, which was-- I don't know what it's called really, but it wasn't on petrol.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't on, on diesel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was the specialty of the German army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They managed to run trucks on, on wood fuel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the exhaust pipe, the exhaust of the truck was coming through on a big-- on a big-- a sort of cylinder inside.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they could-- they-- when there was no need for it, then it was just an ordinary exhaust pipe.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If there was a need for it, it was-- the truck was locked up and, and went in-- all the gas went into the truck in the back.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a gas furnace, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
